---
title: Carb Smart Pepper Pesto Beef Stew with Carrots and Green Peppers
description: A low starch twist on goulash — this stew has hearty beef, loads of veggies, a bit of hearty potato and a swirl of roasted pepper pesto! This bright dollop takes the place of powdered paprika!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-boeuf-au-pesto-de-poivrons-97fa35b5.jpg
